and brought up in sort

00:29:00.900 --> 00:29:04.150
of a deeply religious and
deeply devout atmosphere.

00:29:04.150 --> 00:29:07.370
And I thought, you know, it's easy
to use those people as targets,

00:29:07.370 --> 00:29:09.470
especially if you're
from the East Coast.

00:29:09.470 --> 00:29:11.190
And I thought no that wears itself

00:29:11.190 --> 00:29:13.140
out in about, you know,
two sentences.

00:29:13.140 --> 00:29:15.500
So I thought -- because
actually the people I know

00:29:15.500 --> 00:29:20.450
