00:29:34.150 --> 00:29:37.980
of homeschooled people have
a genuine sort of optimism

00:29:37.980 --> 00:29:39.800
about them that I really admire.

00:29:39.800 --> 00:29:43.980
And in that case with that piece
it was also about what's going

00:29:43.980 --> 00:29:48.890 position:56%
on all the time on today's campuses,
