no, no that's what that college life

00:29:58.750 --> 00:30:00.060
and that age is all about.

00:30:00.060 --> 00:30:03.640
I think you are allowed to
say absurd and strident things

00:30:03.640 --> 00:30:04.960
and find your way in the world.

00:30:04.960 --> 00:30:07.340
At the same time your heart goes

00:30:07.340 --> 00:30:10.200
out to the professors
who have to deal with.

00:30:10.200 --> 00:30:14.090
There was that one student at Yale
who kept howling at a professor

00:30:14.090 --> 00:30:15.840
