00:31:07.960 --> 00:31:10.170
It's funny there was -- well
one thing that happened once

00:31:10.170 --> 00:31:13.690
when I was called in to overhaul
the First Wives Club the movie.

00:31:13.690 --> 00:31:17.010 position:56%
And when I was -- the script I was
given there had been many drafts was

00:31:17.010 --> 00:31:21.140
very serious believe it or
not given the final movie.

00:31:21.140 --> 00:31:24.900
And I remember one of the features
of it if you've seen the film,

00:31:24.900 --> 00:31:28.050
Diane Keaton has a daughter
in it who is a lesbian.

00:31:28.050 --> 00:31:31.860
And in the original draft that
character was mentally disabled

00:31:31.860 --> 00:31:36.870
and she was the word back then used
was retarded and they said Paul,

00:31:36.870 --> 00:31:39.750
could you please make this
character into a lesbian.

00:31:39.750 --> 00:31:42.550
And I kind of by of course
being an idiot I first said,

00:31:42.550 --> 00:31:43.860
well why not both.

00:31:43.860 --> 00:31:48.220
But it was just the
most absurd leap,

00:31:48.220 --> 00:31:52.460 position:56%
but on the other hand they had these
wonderful stars and I went to work

00:31:52.460 --> 00:31:54.720
