00:31:54.720 --> 00:31:58.190
And I thought okay, how do
you turn this tragic story

00:31:58.190 --> 00:32:00.360
of these women who'd been
treated badly by their husbands

00:32:00.360 --> 00:32:04.050
and abandoned into this
sort of powerful statement

00:32:04.050 --> 00:32:08.910
about these women's friendship
and revenge and Manhattan lives.

00:32:08.910 --> 00:32:12.080
So it -- and when, it's a
tribute to the film's producer,

00:32:12.080 --> 00:32:15.500
a guy named Scott Rudin who's
a genius because it was --

00:32:15.500 --> 00:32:18.700
the whole shoot was insane,
nobody was getting along,

00:32:18.700 --> 00:32:20.880
