all sorts of problems.

00:32:20.880 --> 00:32:23.560
And I thought this thing is doomed.

00:32:23.560 --> 00:32:28.360 position:56%
And I told Scott, I said I can't see
this once it opens it's just going

00:32:28.360 --> 00:32:29.970
to be too god-awful.

00:32:29.970 --> 00:32:32.680
And he said he'd been working on
it personally then for a long,

00:32:32.680 --> 00:32:35.390
long time and he said okay, you
have to come see it at least once,

00:32:35.390 --> 00:32:36.900
you have to come to the opening.

00:32:36.900 --> 00:32:40.430
And I said oh all right
and it's delightful.

00:32:40.430 --> 00:32:43.880 position:56%
I mean thanks to the director and to
Scott and to editing and everything

00:32:43.880 --> 00:32:47.400
that can be done in movies and it's
