00:32:51.560 --> 00:32:55.350
So it was -- again, it's the kind
of thing where it's very hard

00:32:55.350 --> 00:32:59.000
to duplicate that process to say
okay, how do I take something

00:32:59.000 --> 00:33:02.870
in big trouble and save it,
but it sure worked that time.

00:33:02.870 --> 00:33:07.620
So it was -- so since then I go
